# Nanobanana Pro — 10 промптов для фоновых слайдов

> **Стиль:** ретро-футуризм 70–80-х, инженерная графика, чертежи, научная фантастика, космос, электроника
> **Палитра:** тёмно-синяя/голубая, редкие оранжевые акценты
> **Пропорции:** 16:9, рисунок — в полях 25% по краям (стилизованная рамка), центр — нейтральная зона для текста

---

## Слайд 1 — «Титульный: Запуск миссии»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi style. The artwork forms a thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approximately 50% width × 50% height of the image). The border area contains: a massive blueprint-style rocket launch platform seen from above with engineering grid lines, technical cross-sections of a rocket engine, scattered electronic circuit traces glowing in cyan and deep blue, thin orange trajectory arcs marking a launch path upward into a starfield. The center zone is left clean and dark (deep navy blue gradient) with no text or graphics. Color palette: predominantly dark navy, steel blue, cyan line-art, with sparse glowing orange accent lines. Style: flat vector meets technical illustration, visible construction lines, dimension annotations (without readable text), hatching patterns, analog computer-era aesthetic. No text, no labels, no watermarks.

---

## Слайд 2 — «Проблема: Хаос данных»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi blueprint style. The artwork forms a thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approximately 50% width × 50% height). The border area depicts: tangled circuits and broken data streams represented as chaotic blueprint wiring diagrams, fragmented punch-card patterns, scattered electronic component symbols (resistors, capacitors, transistors) floating in disarray, old CRT monitors displaying static — all rendered in technical line-art. Thin structural grid overlays the composition. The center is left clean dark navy-blue. Color palette: deep navy, dark teal, cyan wireframes, occasional glowing orange spark accents on broken connections. Style: engineering schematic meets cosmic debris field, analog hatch-shading, 1970s NASA manual aesthetic. No text, no labels.

---

## Слайд 3 — «Решение: ИИ-ассистент»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi style. Thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approx 50%×50%). The border depicts: a stylized humanoid silhouette head in profile rendered as a transparent blueprint cross-section revealing internal circuit boards and glowing neural pathways, surrounded by orbiting data satellites and antenna arrays drawn in technical drafting style, thin concentric radar circles emanating outward, electronic component footprints (IC chips, DIP packages) arranged symmetrically. The center zone is clean dark gradient. Color palette: dark indigo, steel blue, bright cyan technical lines, rare orange glowing nodes at key neural intersection points. Style: vintage technical manual illustration, engineering cross-hatching, retro computer graphics grid. No text, no labels.

