## Слайд 4 — «Анализ CRM: Потоки данных»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi blueprint style. Thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approx 50%×50%). The border area shows: elaborate data flow diagrams rendered as blueprint pipe-and-valve schematics, streams of binary-like patterns flowing through transparent tubes, retro database cylinders connected by glowing circuit traces, a stylized funnel structure filtering data-dots from large to refined — all drawn in engineering drafting style with dimension lines and section markers. Vintage oscilloscope waveforms decorate the corners. Center zone is clean dark space. Color palette: deep navy, cobalt blue, cyan linework, orange accent dots marking data transformation points. Style: 1970s systems engineering manual, analog plotter output aesthetic. No text, no labels.

