## Слайд 5 — «Электронные компоненты: Поставки»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi style. Thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approx 50%×50%). The border depicts: oversized technical drawings of electronic components — integrated circuits with visible die layouts, capacitors in cross-section, PCB trace patterns, connector pinout diagrams — all arranged as a symmetrical decorative composition. Small cargo spacecraft shaped like chip packages travel along glowing supply chain routes between space stations. Thin gridlines and coordinate markers throughout. Center zone is clean dark gradient. Color palette: dark navy, deep blue, cyan component outlines, orange accent glow on supply route paths. Style: vintage electronics datasheet meets space logistics map, precise technical linework, retro blueprint aesthetic. No text, no labels.

