## Слайд 10 — «Финальный: Будущее / CTA»

**Prompt:**
A wide 16:9 dark background illustration in retro-futuristic 1970s–1980s sci-fi blueprint style. Thick decorative border frame around a clear empty center zone (approx 50%×50%). The border area shows: a sweeping cosmic panorama rendered in technical illustration style — distant galaxies as spiral blueprint diagrams, a futuristic city skyline on a planetary horizon drawn in engineering cross-section, a lone spacecraft silhouette ascending toward a bright star, electronic constellation patterns connecting stars like circuit nodes. Perspective grid converging toward the horizon. Gentle aurora-like gradient bands in the border. Center zone is clean dark space with subtle radial glow. Color palette: deep midnight blue, dark indigo, cyan cosmic linework, warm orange glow from the distant star and city lights. Style: vintage sci-fi book cover meets engineering poster, romantic space exploration aesthetic, precise technical linework. No text, no labels.
